            <p class="text-white">Python for Everybody is designed to introduce students to programming and software development through the lens of exploring data.</p>
            <%= link_to 'Explore more', posts_path, class:'btnc' %>
          </div>
          <img class="img-fluid w-100 divs imgc" src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181671/pexels-photo-1181671.jpeg"  width="100vw" height="625" alt="First slide">
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-item px-0 col-12 bg">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h1 class="head bold ">The BookShelve Readers</h1>
